PROFILE
-------
Teilweise hat es immer noch in der oberen Schneedecke diverse harte Schichten, welche druch ganz d&#252;nne Schwachsichten unterbrochen sind.

RUTSCHBLOCK
-----------
Die Schicht von 112 auf 108 cm wurde zum Rutschblock hin immer harter (bis zu H&#228;rte 5) und dicker. Bruch unterhalb dieser harten Schicht.</slf:text></slf:profiletext></slf:profiletext-list></caaml:customData></caaml:metaData><caaml:timeRef><caaml:recordTime><caaml:TimeInstant><caaml:timePosition>2008-03-28T15:00:00+01:00</caaml:timePosition></caaml:TimeInstant></caaml:recordTime><caaml:dateTimeReport>2008-03-28T17:01:56+01:00</caaml:dateTimeReport><caaml:dateTimeLastEdit>2008-03-28T17:23:14+01:00</caaml:dateTimeLastEdit></caaml:timeRef><caaml:srcRef/><caaml:locRef><caaml:name>Saas-Grund, Hohsaas</caaml:name><caaml:validElevation><caaml:ElevationPosition uom="m"><caaml:position>3190</caaml:position></caaml:ElevationPosition></caaml:validElevation><caaml:validAspect><caaml:AspectPosition><caaml:position>NW</caaml:position></caaml:AspectPosition></caaml:validAspect><caaml:validSlopeAngle><caaml:SlopeAnglePosition uom="deg"><caaml:position>32</caaml:position></caaml:SlopeAnglePosition></caaml:validSlopeAngle><caaml:pointLocation><gml:Point id="pointID" srsName="urn:ogc:def:crs:OGC:1.3:CRS84" srsDimension="2"><gml:pos>7.995682 46.141429</gml:pos></gml:Point></caaml:pointLocation></caaml:locRef><caaml:snowProfileResultsOf><caaml:SnowProfileMeasurements dir="top down"><caaml:profileDepth uom="cm">123.0</caaml:profileDepth><caaml:weatherCond><caaml:airTempPres uom="degC">-7.7</caaml:airTempPres></caaml:weatherCond><caaml:snowPackCond><caaml:hS><caaml:Components><caaml:height uom="cm">123.0</caaml:height></caaml:Components></caaml:hS></caaml:snowPackCond><caaml:stratProfile><caaml:Layer><caaml:depthTop uom="cm">0.0</caaml:depthTop><caaml:thickness uom="cm">11.0</caaml:thickness><caaml:wetness uom="">D</caaml:wetness><caaml:grainFormPrimary>PP</caaml:grainFormPrimary><caaml:grainFormSecondary>DF</caaml:grainFormSecondary><caaml:grainSize uom="mm"><caaml:Components><caaml:avg>1.0</caaml:avg></caaml:Components></caaml:grainSize><caaml:hardness uom="">F</caaml:hardness></ca